    "This includes teaching educators how to utilize these technologies effectively, as well as adjusting the curriculum to include AI-driven learning modules [160].",
    "Ensuring equitable access to such advanced AI tools will be essential to bridge educational gap and foster a more inclusive learning environment.The present study has certain limitations.",
    "Firstly, this study is a narrative review, which lacks the structured approach of a systematic review.",
    "This approach was necessary due to the limited research available on generative AI specifically within orthopedic education.",
    "Limited data on long-term impacts of generative AI in orthopedic education due to the technology's nascent state and the lack of longitudinal studies or controlled trials in this area specific to orthopedic education limits the ability to draw definitive conclusions about the long-term effectiveness of generative AI applications in orthopedic training.Another limitation of this study could be potential biases in the literature review due to the rapidly evolving nature of this field."
